Package org.jdrupes.httpcodec.types

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Converter<T>
    Implemented by classes that convert between a value and its string representation in the HTTP header field.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractParamValueConverter<T>
    A base class for converters for values with parameters.
    Converters
    Utility methods and constants for converters.
    ListConverter<T>
    Used by by classes that convert field values which consist of lists of values.
    MediaType  
    MediaType.Builder
    A builder for the (immutable) parameterized type.
    MediaType.MediaMainType
    Represents a media type, including a media range (type or subtype equals “*”).
    ParameterizedValue<T>
    Represents a parameterized value such as value; param1=value1; param2=value2.
    ParameterizedValue.Builder<T>
    A builder for the (immutable) parameterized type.
    ParameterizedValueConverter<T>
    Extends AbstractParamValueConverter to a realization of Converter<ParameterizedValue<T>>.
